    Thrash was tearing across the landscape, his metallic fins sawing
through trees and other foilage when he came upon a rather odd scene. Three
bots outside a stasis pod were talking, the stasis pod itself seemed
undamaged and appeared open. Even as the giant shark transformed landing a
small distance from the group a laser pistol appeared in his hand, a minor
weapon compared to what two of the bots seemed to carry but such facts
nevered deterred Thrash, slowly he approached keeping his eyes on all and
none, &quot;Who are you bots?&quot;
